React Native Background Actions --Library--
In this library there is an important integration in androidManifest file which is not mentioned on their site. 
we need to add this piece of code  <service android:name="com.asterinet.react.bgactions.RNBackgroundActionsTask" /> as shown below.
  </activity>
       <service android:name="com.asterinet.react.bgactions.RNBackgroundActionsTask" />
  </application>
